msgid ":ref:`a_references` - Recommended Reading"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/int_overview.rst:74
msgid "This chapter explains how you organise your notes, and how the Tags and References system works. This system lets you cross-link your documents in your project, and display these references in the application interface."
msgstr ""

